---
// ChainsVsLoops.astro — Pure CSS side-by-side animation
// Chains: linear pass, breaks on one bad step. Loops: re-route, recover, retry.
---

<div class="cvl-wrap">
  <h3 class="cvl-title">The Race: Chain vs Loop</h3>
  <p class="cvl-sub">Same 5 tasks. Chain goes straight. Loop adapts. Watch what happens when step 3 fails.</p>

  <div class="cvl-lanes">
    <!-- Chain lane -->
    <div class="cvl-lane">
      <div class="cvl-label cvl-label--red">⛓ Chain (Sequential)</div>
      <div class="cvl-track">
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--chain">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 1</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--green" style="animation-delay: 0s"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--green" style="animation-delay: 0.8s">✓</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cvl-arrow cvl-arrow--green">→</div>
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--chain">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 2</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--green" style="animation-delay: 1.2s"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--green" style="animation-delay: 2.0s">✓</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cvl-arrow cvl-arrow--green">→</div>
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--chain cvl-step--fail">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 3</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--red" style="animation-delay: 2.4s"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--red" style="animation-delay: 3.2s">✗</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cvl-arrow cvl-arrow--dead">✗</div>
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--chain cvl-step--dead">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 4</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--dead"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--dead">—</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cvl-arrow cvl-arrow--dead">✗</div>
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--chain cvl-step--dead">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 5</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--dead"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--dead">—</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cvl-verdict cvl-verdict--red">
        <strong>CRASHED at Step 3.</strong> Steps 4–5 never ran. State lost.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Loop lane -->
    <div class="cvl-lane">
      <div class="cvl-label cvl-label--green">🔄 Loop (LangGraph StateGraph)</div>
      <div class="cvl-track">
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--loop">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 1</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--green" style="animation-delay: 0s"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--green" style="animation-delay: 0.6s">✓</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cvl-arrow cvl-arrow--green">→</div>
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--loop">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 2</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--green" style="animation-delay: 0.8s"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--green" style="animation-delay: 1.4s">✓</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cvl-arrow cvl-arrow--green">→</div>
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--loop cvl-step--retry">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 3</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--amber" style="animation-delay: 1.6s"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--amber" style="animation-delay: 2.2s">↻</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cvl-arrow cvl-arrow--amber">↻</div>
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--loop">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Step 3*</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--green" style="animation-delay: 2.4s"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--green" style="animation-delay: 3.0s">✓</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cvl-arrow cvl-arrow--green">→</div>
        <div class="cvl-step cvl-step--loop">
          <div class="cvl-step-id">Steps 4–5</div>
          <div class="cvl-step-bar"><div class="cvl-fill cvl-fill--green" style="animation-delay: 3.2s"></div></div>
          <div class="cvl-check cvl-check--green" style="animation-delay: 3.8s">✓✓</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cvl-verdict cvl-verdict--green">
        <strong>Self-healed at Step 3.</strong> State preserved. All steps completed.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cvl-insight">
    <div class="cvl-insight-icon">🔑</div>
    <div>Chains break at the first failure. Loops <strong>carry state forward</strong>, re-route, and keep going. That's the core of LangGraph's StateGraph.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .cvl-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .cvl-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .cvl-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .cvl-lanes { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .cvl-lanes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .cvl-lane {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .cvl-label {
    font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;
  }
  .cvl-label--red { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.12); color: #f87171; }
  .cvl-label--green { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.12); color: #4ade80; }

  .cvl-track { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .cvl-step {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 4px; min-width: 50px;
  }
  .cvl-step-id { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; color: #64748b; }
  .cvl-step-bar { width: 50px; height: 8px; background: #1e293b; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .cvl-fill {
    height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; width: 0%;
    animation: cvl-bar 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .cvl-fill--green { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e, #4ade80); }
  .cvl-fill--red { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f87171); }
  .cvl-fill--amber { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f59e0b, #fbbf24); }
  .cvl-fill--dead { background: #334155; width: 100%; opacity: 0.3; }
  @keyframes cvl-bar { to { width: 100%; } }

  .cvl-check {
    font-size: 0.65rem; opacity: 0;
    animation: cvl-pop 0.3s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .cvl-check--green { color: #4ade80; }
  .cvl-check--red { color: #f87171; }
  .cvl-check--amber { color: #f59e0b; }
  .cvl-check--dead { color: #475569; opacity: 0.4; animation: none; }
  @keyframes cvl-pop { from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); } to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } }

  .cvl-arrow { font-size: 0.6rem; font-family: monospace; }
  .cvl-arrow--green { color: #4ade8060; }
  .cvl-arrow--amber { color: #f59e0b80; }
  .cvl-arrow--dead { color: #ef444440; }

  .cvl-step--fail { }
  .cvl-step--dead { opacity: 0.35; }
  .cvl-step--retry { }

  .cvl-verdict {
    margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;
  }
  .cvl-verdict--red { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.06); color: #f87171; border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.15); }
  .cvl-verdict--green { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.06); color: #4ade80; border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.15); }

  .cvl-insight {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(74,222,128,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.15); border-radius: 10px;
    color: #cbd5e1; font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .cvl-insight strong { color: #4ade80; }
  .cvl-insight-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
</style>
